  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Freelance Hairdresser",
  "description": "<p>TONI&GUY Duxton is a boutique, premium hair salon located in the Duxton area. We are seeking <strong>experienced freelance hairstylists</strong> who are confident handling clients independently and <strong>have an existing customer base</strong>.</p><p>This role is suitable for freelancers who are looking for a <strong>professional, structured salon environment</strong> to serve and grow their own clientele.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle clients independently for <strong>haircut, colour, and treatment services</strong></p></li><li><p>Conduct professional consultations and recommend suitable services and aftercare</p></li><li><p>Deliver consistent service quality aligned with salon standards</p></li><li><p>Maintain hygiene, professionalism, and time management on the salon floor</p></li><li><p>Work collaboratively within a shared salon environment and follow operational guidelines</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Minimum 5 years of experience handling clients independently</strong> in a salon environment</p></li><li><p>Strong technical competence in <strong>cut, colour, and treatment services</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Existing customer base is required</strong></p></li><li><p>Hairdressing certification or equivalent professional training preferred</p></li><li><p>Good communication and client management skills</p></li><li><p>Professional attitude, reliability, and respect for shared salon operations</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working on a freelance basis </p></li></ul><p><strong>Compensation & Benefits</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Tiered commission structure with clear progression</strong>, where commission rates increase as monthly service revenue grows</p></li><li><p>Transparent cost structure</p></li><li><p>Fully equipped boutique salon in a central location</p></li><li><p>Use of salon booking system and operational support</p></li><li><p>Professional, well-maintained working environment</p></li></ul>",
